text: The 1110s was a decade that began on 1 January 1110, and ended on 31 December 1119. It is distinct from the decade known as the 112th decade which began on January 1, 1111 and ended on December 31, 1120. == Events and trends == * 1111 Henry V is crowned Holy Roman Emperor by Pope Paschal II * 1112 The people of Laon, France, proclaim a commune and murder their bishop * 1113 Pierre Ab√©lard opens his school in Paris * 1119 Knights Templar Order established in Jerusalem
